(1)Alexander Avenue, east side, north from East 140th Street. At the south east corner of East 141st Street is the Alexander Avenue Baptist Church. Beyond that can be seen the spire of St. Mary's Episcopal Church, at 141st Street.

(2)is north from East 141st Street.

(3)shows a closeup of the Alexander Avenue Baptist Church.

P. L. Sperr


View 1: November 14, 1937
View 2,3 April 29, 1941
